📘 Assignment – 2

🎯 Objective:
Write a Python program to display 10 lines about your favourite leader using variables.

📝 Instructions:

1. Choose your favourite leader.
2. Create variables to store information about the leader.
3. Use `print()` statements to display the information.
4. Display at least 10 lines.

📌 Example Output:

Name: Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam
Born: 15 October 1931
Country: India
Profession: Scientist
Known As: Missile Man of India
Award: Bharat Ratna
Dream: Developed India
Quality: Hardworking
Inspiration: Millions of Students
Favourite Quote: Dream, Dream, Dream

💾 Submission:
• Save the file as `assignment2-yourname.py`
• Example: `assignment2-rahul.py`
• Run the program and verify the output.

✅ This assignment will help you practice *variables* and *print()* statements in Python.
